<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>107</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh vancung a um nain Vaw lei cungah a rung tum, Mi vialte ca a rung
 tum i, A zawmi a damter hna, Baibal ca chungin na hngalh lai, Mitha
 mingan bik a si.

[V2]
 Khua vialte ah aa chok lengmang, Mi vialte a zaangfah hna, Mithalo,
 tlu-kiak vialte le, Mitcaw, kebei, mithi mi, A bia in a damter than ca,
 Khuaruahhar ngaingai a si.

[V3]
 Jesuh vawlei a um lio ah, Tha chin bia lawng a chimh hna, Keimah zong
 Jesuh ka zum i, Ka lunglawmhnak a um cang, Ka zumh sualnak kha Pathian
 nih, Tha tein a ka remhpiak.

[V4]
 Thachin a kan pek Pathian nih, Jesuh nih a kan chimh cang, Mi a cheu
 nih khan an zumh i, A cheu nih an zum ve lo, A zum lomi nih sifahnak,
 Jesuh bia bang an in lai.

[V5]
 Keimah caah Bawi Jesuh cu, Vailamtahnak ah a thi, Amah hawi nih khan
 an vui i, Ni thum hnuah a tho than, Vancung khua chungah a um i, Mi
 vialte a zaangfah hna.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>A SUALMI HNA RA U CH107</title>
</song>